We are located in the Handy Networks data center in the heart of downtown Denver, Colorado with excellent speeds and latency to every corner of the country and globe! We own all of our own equipment and have offices in the same building as our data center.

Every Linux 512MB and 1GB LET Special VPS Plan we sell includes a free DirectAdmin license for the life of the service you have with Mean Servers along with the initial install for FREE. All of our servers boast the newest generation of components made by leading brands such as Dell and HP. Mean Servers NEVER oversells and keeps a cloud platform making it easy to move your VPS to a new node if you wish to upgrade your plan. Every VPS plan also includes access to our SolusVM VPS Control Panel allowing our clients to reboot, shutdown, VNC, change root passwords, and reload the operating system without intervention from us. All of our VPS plans utilize KVM technology giving you privacy, speed, guaranteed resources, and root access.

